                        "text_blocks": [
                            {
                                "start": 721.164,
                                "stop": 744.719,
                                "byte_start": 2988178,
                                "byte_stop": 3082324,
                                "text": "-- course of your argument if I asked whether in any proceedings, between the United States and the owner of the condemned land, with the outstanding flowage interest of the respondents here, whatever that is that may have been deemed to be ever made its appearance in the process by which the imminent domain transaction is completed."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 744.719,
                        "stop": 810.743,
                        "byte_start": 3082324,
                        "byte_stop": 3346474,
                        "speaker": {
                            "ID": 38135,
                            "name": "Perry W. Morton",
                            "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/people\/perry_w_morton",
                            "last_name": "Morton",
                            "roles": null,
                            "thumbnail": null,
                            "length_of_service": 0,
                            "identifier": "perry_w_morton"
                        },
                        "text_blocks": [
                            {
                                "start": 744.719,
                                "stop": 753.007,
                                "byte_start": 3082324,
                                "byte_stop": 3115551,
                                "text": "The complaint simply describes and the declaration of taking to at the earliest part of the record."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 753.007,
                                "stop": 774.219,
                                "byte_start": 3115551,
                                "byte_stop": 3200397,
                                "text": "The nature of the estate which the Government wanted that is to flow permanently or intermittently and so on and so on and so on over certain described parcels which were set out in appendix to the complaint by a full legal description."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 774.219,
                                "stop": 784.367,
                                "byte_start": 3200397,
                                "byte_stop": 3240939,
                                "text": "And the -- the parties are then named as parties having an interest or a possible interest in the property."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 784.367,
                                "stop": 805.522,
                                "byte_start": 3240939,
                                "byte_stop": 3325576,
                                "text": "I would recall to you perhaps the 93-acre case, the Illinois Aircraft case about two years ago now in which you said of course that the mere jointer of a party, the mere bringing of a domain proceeding against a party is not necessarily a recognition of an interest that that party may have."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 805.522,
                                "stop": 810.743,
                                "byte_start": 3325576,
                                "byte_stop": 3346474,
                                "text": "This forum may be tested to determine the existence of such an interest."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 810.743,
                        "stop": 814.37,
                        "byte_start": 3346474,
                        "byte_stop": 3360893,
                        "speaker": {
                            "ID": 15099,
                            "name": "Earl Warren",
                            "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/people\/earl_warren",
                            "last_name": "Warren",
                            "roles": [
                                {
